I was drawing pictures of
Goldie, what she might look

00:18:55.296 --> 00:18:58.476 A:middle
like building machines,
using thread spools and clay,

00:18:58.476 --> 00:19:00.526 A:middle
stuff around the house,
the hardware store,


WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:18:58.476 --> 00:19:00.526 A:middle
stuff around the house,
the hardware store,

00:19:00.816 --> 00:19:02.826 A:middle
until finally I had
a working prototype.

00:19:02.936 --> 00:19:06.906 A:middle
And it was the ugliest
thing you have ever seen,

00:19:07.296 --> 00:19:08.836 A:middle
but it worked and I was excited.

00:19:08.836 --> 00:19:12.596 A:middle
And so I finally decided I'm
