to the New York Toy
Fair and I'm going

00:19:14.406 --> 00:19:17.256 A:middle
to see what the industry
has to say.

00:19:17.306 --> 00:19:22.416 A:middle
So I went to the show with my
prototype and a badge I managed

00:19:22.516 --> 00:19:25.486 A:middle
to finagle, pretty
much snuck in,

00:19:25.486 --> 00:19:27.496 A:middle
and a giant stack
of NDAs, of course.

00:19:28.576 --> 00:19:31.096 A:middle
And started walking
around booth to booth,

00:19:31.296 --> 00:19:33.806 A:middle
talking with everyone I
could, toy store owners,

00:19:34.006 --> 00:19:37.996 A:middle
toy executives, other
toy inventors to try

00:19:37.996 --> 00:19:40.946 A:middle
to get their feedback on what
they thought of my genius idea,

00:19:41.366 --> 00:19:42.796 A:middle
the engineering toy for girls.

00:19:43.586 --> 00:19:47.326 A:middle
Well, the response
was pretty unanimous,

00:19:48.876 --> 00:19:50.066 A:middle
you can't fight nature.

00:19:50.776 --> 00:19:55.596 A:middle
Again, these people, they
