00:20:15.756 --> 00:20:19.256 A:middle
They said maybe if you're
lucky you can license your idea

00:20:19.336 --> 00:20:22.986 A:middle
to some little educational
toy reseller

00:20:22.986 --> 00:20:25.266 A:middle
who maybe can convince
a school to put it in,

00:20:26.186 --> 00:20:28.356 A:middle
but starting your own company,

00:20:28.746 --> 00:20:30.846 A:middle
trying to make this
go mainstream,

00:20:31.216 --> 00:20:34.496 A:middle
it's an uphill battle and
you're never going to win it.

