Now I was feeling pretty
dejected after Toy Fair and,


WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:20:56.646 --> 00:21:00.286 A:middle
Now I was feeling pretty
dejected after Toy Fair and,

00:21:00.336 --> 00:21:02.626 A:middle
honestly, I wasn't
really in the mood to go

