But at the same time
it was pretty rough,

00:33:04.506 --> 00:33:08.276 A:middle
we started to get sales reports
in, and just because you're

00:33:08.276 --> 00:33:10.436 A:middle
in Toys R Us nationwide
doesn't mean

00:33:10.436 --> 00:33:13.646 A:middle
that people are necessarily
going to buy it.

00:33:13.816 --> 00:33:18.116 A:middle
And it wasn't looking good,
the toys weren't selling.

00:33:18.116 --> 00:33:20.766 A:middle
So we asked the Toys R Us
team, you know, what can we do,

00:33:20.766 --> 00:33:22.926 A:middle
how do we get more
people to buy GoldieBlox?

00:33:23.466 --> 00:33:25.476 A:middle
And they said, well, most brands

00:33:25.476 --> 00:33:29.886 A:middle
in our store will do national
TV advertising for a minimum

00:33:29.886 --> 00:33:31.686 A:middle
of a $2 million buy, you know,

00:33:31.686 --> 00:33:33.116 A:middle
you might be able
to move the needle.

00:33:34.316 --> 00:33:35.486 A:middle
Two million dollars?

00:33:36.536 --> 00:33:39.846 A:middle
That was definitely
not an option, right?

00:33:40.266 --> 00:33:42.716 A:middle
But we did have 5,000
Kickstarter backers

00:33:43.166 --> 00:33:45.526 A:middle
and we had my husband, Beau,
who knew how to make a video.

00:33:46.316 --> 00:33:49.466 A:middle
So we decided we've got to
make our own commercial.

00:33:49.796 --> 00:33:52.106 A:middle
And maybe we can't put it
on TV, but you know what,

00:33:52.106 --> 00:33:53.526 A:middle
we can put it up on YouTube.

00:33:54.116 --> 00:33:56.636 A:middle
So we're going to disrupt
the pink aisle ourselves.

00:33:57.906 --> 00:34:01.536 A:middle
We reached out to all of our
Kickstarter backers and we came


WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:33:57.906 --> 00:34:01.536 A:middle
We reached out to all of our
Kickstarter backers and we came

00:34:01.536 --> 00:34:05.806 A:middle
up with this idea, let's shoot
a video having girls rampaging

00:34:05.806 --> 00:34:07.516 A:middle
through the pink
aisle at Toys R Us,

00:34:08.146 --> 00:34:12.106 A:middle
singing "We Are The Champions,"
like this is awesome.

00:34:12.696 --> 00:34:15.085 A:middle
So we called up our Kickstarter
backers, and we said meet us

00:34:15.085 --> 00:34:17.636 A:middle
in the parking lot of Toys
R Us, we've got an idea.

00:34:18.846 --> 00:34:20.766 A:middle
So about 50 kids and
their parents showed

