zoetrope with our pieces.

00:45:12.506 --> 00:45:15.186 A:middle
The pieces are inspired by
common household objects,

00:45:15.886 --> 00:45:19.686 A:middle
stuff from the hardware store,
the arts and crafts section.

00:45:19.916 --> 00:45:21.886 A:middle
What helps with making
these pieces feel

00:45:21.886 --> 00:45:24.086 A:middle
like common household
objects is it makes kids start

00:45:24.086 --> 00:45:25.756 A:middle
to see the world
as their toolbox,

00:45:25.756 --> 00:45:27.586 A:middle
that they can really
invent anything.

00:45:27.586 --> 00:45:30.476 A:middle
But then what really
brings the experience

00:45:30.546 --> 00:45:34.706 A:middle
to life is our mobile app,
with drawing tools, stamps,

00:45:35.186 --> 00:45:37.396 A:middle
stop motion photography
and backgrounds,

00:45:37.796 --> 00:45:40.096 A:middle
kids can make their
own movies digitally,

00:45:40.466 --> 00:45:43.476 A:middle
and then they can air print
them if they want to play

00:45:43.586 --> 00:45:46.246 A:middle
in their actual zoetrope
movie machine device,

00:45:46.756 --> 00:45:48.646 A:middle
they can email them,
they can text them,

00:45:49.176 --> 00:45:51.716 A:middle
or they can even send
it to the Apple Watch.

00:45:52.516 --> 00:45:59.576 A:middle
[ Applause ]


